{"tid":871134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國國防大臣韋廉信稱堅決支持美國退出中程導彈條約","createTime":"2018-10-21T16:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T16:47:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d521561ad987df351c19abf461b7445ffd269b","tid":871134,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1424076_1_L_20181021235425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1424076_1_L_20181021235425.jpg&h=9b8ad453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國國防大臣韋廉信說，堅決支持美國打算退出《中程導彈條約》的決定。<br />\n<br />\n韋廉信批評俄羅斯損害該條約，呼籲克里姆林宮應處理好自己的問題，又形容美國是英國長期關係密切的盟友，英方支持美方透過今次決定，敦促俄羅斯尊重該條約的義務。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前揚言，美國會退出美俄之間在前蘇聯時代簽署生效的《中程導彈條約》，指責俄方違反條約在先。俄羅斯批評美國的做法是為了追求「單極世界」，但不可能實現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424076-20181021.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424076-20181021.htm&d=m%2B0%2BLbE%2FOxXva2acS8PPQdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b59a7a74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424076-20181021.htm&h=807f6b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424076-20181021.htm</a>"},{"pid":"04879954652376abbed8d579e5f817455e00c3c1","tid":871134,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"佢老婆任務失敗 會唔會俾中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c012ec7069e4840e4f505ef6233c33a9b87f66","tid":871134,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04879954652376abbed8d579e5f817455e00c3c1","tid":871134,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-